metadata.description:
For the #FIRST Time in History, Numismatics Meets Cryptocurrency Head-on!

Introducing the infusion of Numismatic Digital Art/Motion Graphics and NFTs! This is as real as real-world utility gets. Offering more than just a single artistic digital asset for your collection, here we find the opportunity for history in the making, coupled with state-of-the-art Crypto technology, and the potential to acquire a Certified Rare Coin.

The #FIRST 3rd Party-graded Certified rare coin offered from #ThePoobahCollection, in conjunction with INFINITE OBJECTS. This creative collaborative initiative allows for the tangible representation of your digital art via NFT Video Print technology. Keep the NFT in your Wallet, and showcase it in your home or office! The NFT Video Print will be shipped to the Recipient (nationally/internationally) free of charge.

Additionally, the open release of the Coin's TPG Certification is on the line! Should the auction price realized exceed twice the TPG Price Guide Value of the rare coin, the Recipient will receive full-rights to the Locked & PCGS-Secured TPG Cert! Never before has such a power-move been accomplished!

To top it off, the open release of the rare coin itself is on the line! In the event that the auction price realized exceeds three times the TPG PGV, the Recipient may acquire the rare coin as well! Yes, that's right!...the (physical) Certified Rare Coin's ownership will be transferred from the current collection to the Recipient, and shipped accordingly.

The potential exists for formal press release, as this will be a #FIRST, so let's make history!

Check out the details & HI-RES vids at: NumismaticFanaTic.art
